                                  Project: Wolfenstein Part II ( Post-Apocalyptic Earth)          You have now broken out of the prison in which this new breed of Nazis have been  performing test on you only to find outside even worse. This new earth is filled to the brim with death and sickness. You must get to the other side of this so-called city and get out, it will be hard but your hearing is coming back and you have grown stronger. Good luck, you'll need it. May the slaughter rage on.